descriptionHtml:
This colorful keyboard app will personalize and transform your phone, making it unique. Wonderful themes and designs have been created just for you. The new colors will make you smile and feel good. Our exclusive collection of stickers will make you stand out when chatting with your friends.

What you get when you install Change Color of Keypad:

♥ A new awesome background for your keyboard. You can further customize the colors from the theme gallery. Don't forget to turn the key borders on and off before deciding your favorite keyboard layout!

♥ Stickers and GIFs: Express yourself in style with our extensive collection of stickers and GIFs. Choose from a wide range of content to add personality and fun to your chats. Let your creativity run wild and make your messages truly stand out.

♥ Clipboard: Copy-pasting made easy. Our keyboard will automatically suggest texts, URL's that you copied to the clipboard. One-click and boom! your text gets pasted in the chat.

♥ In-Keyboard Browser: Say goodbye to switching between apps. Our in-keyboard browser allows you to search the web, find information, and effortlessly share links while staying in the keyboard interface in your chat. Stay connected and multitask seamlessly without interrupting your conversations.

♥ Limitless Customization: change keyboard size, display numbers row, configure key vibration, sound, language, autocorrect options and more, making your keyboard an extension of your personality.

The keyboard is compatible with all modern Android phones.

With Change Color of Keypad, your mobile communication experience reaches new heights. Say goodbye to mundane keyboards and embrace a world of creativity and style. Download our app now and revolutionize the way you write your messages with Cute Keyboard - your typing companion.
